      • getProgress

        public static ComponentFunction getProgress(java.lang.String winname,
                            java.lang.String compname,
                            java.lang.String variableName,
                            java.lang.String isPrimary)
         
                 Action to get progress of a progress bar component.
        Supporting Engines:

        • Google Android
        Parameters:
        winname - Optional:NO The name of the window to act upon.
        compname - Optional:NO The name of the component to act upon.
        variableName - Optional:NO The variable VariableName will contain the progress of progress bar in percentage.
        isPrimary - Optional:YES IsPrimary is boolean value (default is true). It indicates which indicator to get.

      • getProgress

        public static ComponentFunction getProgress(java.lang.String winname,
                            java.lang.String compname,
                            java.lang.String[] parameters)
         
                 Action to get progress of a progress bar component.
        Supporting Engines:

        • Google Android
        Parameters:
        winname - Optional:NO The name of the window to act upon.
        compname - Optional:NO The name of the component to act upon.
        parameters - Optional:NO An array containing the following parameters:

          variableName -- Optional:NO The variable VariableName will contain the progress of progress bar in percentage.
          isPrimary -- Optional:YES IsPrimary is boolean value (default is true). It indicates which indicator to get.
